{"history_size": 1, "folders": ["practice_week11"], "nr": 1165, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2024-04-09T02:37:45Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "lkqwaip6puf2di", "data": "lurrua4esp55ww", "v": "all", "type": "create", "when": "2024-04-09T02:37:45Z"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "krvaikp4js87pd", "data": "lurtd4ynk2759e", "to": "lurrua4764f5wv", "type": "i_answer", "when": "2024-04-09T03:20:24Z"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "lkqwaip6puf2di", "subject": "Find Eigenvalue for 3 by 3 matrix", "created": "2024-04-09T02:37:45Z", "content": "I was doing a practice a problem in find eigenvalues in week11 problem. When I was working on a 3 by 3 matrix, it is very time consuming, when there is no and 1 in that matrix. Anyone have any suggestion for shortcuts. Thank you.  "}], "type": "question", "tags": ["practice_week11", "student"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 45, "children": [{"history_size": 1, "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2024-04-09T03:20:24Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "krvaikp4js87pd", "subject": "", "created": "2024-04-09T03:20:24Z", "content": "<md>For 3 by 3 matrices, the best shortcut I have is to memorize the determinant of a 2x2 matrix, where

